section Section1;
shared WIP_Class = let
  Source = Oracle.Database("COHREP", [HierarchicalNavigation=true, 
  Query="
  SELECT
   SYSDATE EXTRACT_DATE,
    from_tz(cast (sysdate as timestamp),'PST') at time zone '"&LocalTZ&"' local_extract_date,
   MP.ORGANIZATION_CODE,
   WAC.CLASS_CODE,
   WAC.DESCRIPTION,
   WAC.CLASS_TYPE CLASS_TYPE_CODE,
   WLO.MEANING CLASS_TYPE,
   WAC.DISABLE_DATE,
   MAC.CONCATENATED_SEGMENTS MATERIAL_ACCOUNT,
   MOHAC.CONCATENATED_SEGMENTS MATERIAL_OVERHEAD_ACCOUNT,
   RESAC.CONCATENATED_SEGMENTS RESOURCE_ACCOUNT,
   OHAC.CONCATENATED_SEGMENTS OVERHEAD_ACCOUNT,
   OSPAC.CONCATENATED_SEGMENTS OUTSIDE_PROCESSING_ACCOUNT,
   MVAC.CONCATENATED_SEGMENTS MATERIAL_VARIANCE_ACCOUNT,
   RESVAC.CONCATENATED_SEGMENTS RESOURCE_VARIANCE_ACCOUNT,
   OHVAC.CONCATENATED_SEGMENTS OVERHEAD_VARIANCE_ACCOUNT,
   OSPVAC.CONCATENATED_SEGMENTS OSP_VARIANCE_ACCOUNT,
   SADJAC.CONCATENATED_SEGMENTS STD_COST_ADJ_ACCOUNT,
   WAC.ATTRIBUTE1 WORK_TYPE,
   WAC.ATTRIBUTE2 ACCOUNTING_TYPE,
   WAC.ATTRIBUTE3 ACTIVITY,
   WAC.CREATION_DATE,
   CU.USER_NAME CREATED_BY,
   WAC.LAST_UPDATE_DATE,
   LU.USER_NAME LAST_UPDATED_BY 
FROM
   APPS.FND_USER CU,
   APPS.FND_USER LU,
   APPS.GL_CODE_COMBINATIONS_KFV MAC,
   APPS.GL_CODE_COMBINATIONS_KFV MOHAC,
   APPS.GL_CODE_COMBINATIONS_KFV RESAC,
   APPS.GL_CODE_COMBINATIONS_KFV OHAC,
   APPS.GL_CODE_COMBINATIONS_KFV OSPAC,
   APPS.GL_CODE_COMBINATIONS_KFV MVAC,
   APPS.GL_CODE_COMBINATIONS_KFV OHVAC,
   APPS.GL_CODE_COMBINATIONS_KFV RESVAC,
   APPS.GL_CODE_COMBINATIONS_KFV OSPVAC,
   APPS.GL_CODE_COMBINATIONS_KFV SADJAC,
   APPS.FND_LOOKUP_VALUES WLO,
   APPS.WIP_ACCOUNTING_CLASSES WAC,
   APPS.MTL_PARAMETERS MP 
WHERE
   MP.ORGANIZATION_CODE = '"&ORG&"' 
   AND CU.USER_ID ( + ) = WAC.CREATED_BY 
   AND LU.USER_ID ( + ) = WAC.LAST_UPDATED_BY 
   AND MAC.CODE_COMBINATION_ID ( + ) = WAC.MATERIAL_ACCOUNT 
   AND MOHAC.CODE_COMBINATION_ID ( + ) = WAC.MATERIAL_OVERHEAD_ACCOUNT 
   AND RESAC.CODE_COMBINATION_ID ( + ) = WAC.RESOURCE_ACCOUNT 
   AND OHAC.CODE_COMBINATION_ID ( + ) = WAC.OVERHEAD_ACCOUNT 
   AND OSPAC.CODE_COMBINATION_ID ( + ) = WAC.OUTSIDE_PROCESSING_ACCOUNT 
   AND MVAC.CODE_COMBINATION_ID ( + ) = WAC.MATERIAL_VARIANCE_ACCOUNT 
   AND RESVAC.CODE_COMBINATION_ID ( + ) = WAC.RESOURCE_VARIANCE_ACCOUNT 
   AND OHVAC.CODE_COMBINATION_ID ( + ) = WAC.OVERHEAD_VARIANCE_ACCOUNT 
   AND OSPVAC.CODE_COMBINATION_ID ( + ) = WAC.OUTSIDE_PROC_VARIANCE_ACCOUNT 
   AND SADJAC.CODE_COMBINATION_ID ( + ) = WAC.STD_COST_ADJUSTMENT_ACCOUNT 
   AND WLO.LANGUAGE = 'US' 
   AND WLO.LOOKUP_TYPE = 'WIP_CLASS_TYPE' 
   AND WLO.LOOKUP_CODE = WAC.CLASS_TYPE 
   AND WAC.ORGANIZATION_ID = MP.ORGANIZATION_ID"
, CommandTimeout=#duration(0, 0, 10, 0)]),
  #"Renamed columns" = Table.RenameColumns(Source, {{"ORGANIZATION_CODE", "Organization Code"}, {"CLASS_CODE", "Class Code"}, {"DESCRIPTION", "Class Description"}, {"CLASS_TYPE", "Class Type"}, {"WORK_TYPE", "Work Type"}, {"ACCOUNTING_TYPE", "Accounting Type"}, {"ACTIVITY", "Activity"}, {"MATERIAL_ACCOUNT", "Material Account"}, {"MATERIAL_OVERHEAD_ACCOUNT", "Material Overhead Account"}, {"RESOURCE_ACCOUNT", "Resource Account"}, {"OVERHEAD_ACCOUNT", "Overhead Account"}, {"OUTSIDE_PROCESSING_ACCOUNT", "OSP Account"}, {"MATERIAL_VARIANCE_ACCOUNT", "Material Variance Account"}, {"RESOURCE_VARIANCE_ACCOUNT", "Resource Variance Account"}, {"OVERHEAD_VARIANCE_ACCOUNT", "Overhead Variance Account"}, {"OSP_VARIANCE_ACCOUNT", "OSP Variance Account"}, {"STD_COST_ADJ_ACCOUNT", "Cost Adjustment Account"}, {"CREATION_DATE", "Creation Date"}, {"CREATED_BY", "Created By"}, {"LAST_UPDATE_DATE", "Last Update Date"}, {"LAST_UPDATED_BY", "Last Updated By"}, {"EXTRACT_DATE", "Extract Date"}, {"LOCAL_EXTRACT_DATE", "Local Extract Date"}}),
  ConvertToList = Table.AddColumn(#"Renamed columns", "ClassCodeToList", each Text.ToList([Class Code])),
  LowerCaseChars = {"a".."z"},
  // add Character.FromNumber(8203) to make the column unique
  AddInvisibleChars = Table.AddColumn(ConvertToList, "AddInvisibleChars", each List.Transform(
            [ClassCodeToList], 
            each 
            if 
            List.Contains(#"LowerCaseChars", _) 
            then 
            _ & Character.FromNumber(8203) 
            else _
            )),
  // Add case sensitive column as result of adding invisible characters Character.FromNumber(8203)
  AddCaseSensitiveColumn = Table.AddColumn(AddInvisibleChars, "Class Code CS", each Text.Combine([AddInvisibleChars])),
  #"Removed columns" = Table.RemoveColumns(AddCaseSensitiveColumn, {"ClassCodeToList", "AddInvisibleChars"}),
  #"Changed column type" = Table.TransformColumnTypes(#"Removed columns", {{"Class Code CS", type text}})
in
  #"Changed column type";
shared WIP_Department_Resource = let
  Source = Oracle.Database("COHREP", [HierarchicalNavigation=true, 
  Query="
  select sysdate extract_date,
  from_tz(cast (sysdate as timestamp),'PST') at time zone '"&LocalTZ&"' local_extract_date
,bdept.department_id
,bdept.department_code
,bdept.description department_description
,bdept.location_code
,bdr.resource_id
,bdr.resource_code
,bdr.resource_description
,bdr.unit_of_measure
,crc.resource_rate
,decode(bdr.available_24_hours_flag,1,'Yes',2,'No') hours24_flag
,BRT.MEANING RESOURCE_TYPE
,BACT.MEANING AUTOCHARGE_TYPE
,decode(br.DEFAULT_BASIS_TYPE,1,'Item',2,'Lot') DEFAULT_BASIS_TYPE
from apps.BOM_DEPARTMENTS_V bdept
, apps.mtl_parameters mp
,apps.BOM_DEPARTMENT_RESOURCES_V  bdr
,apps.CST_RESOURCE_COSTS_V crc
,APPS.BOM_RESOURCES_V br
,(SELECT LOOKUP_CODE,MEANING FROM apps.mfg_lookups_v
WHERE lookup_type = 'BOM_RESOURCE_TYPE') BRT
,(SELECT LOOKUP_CODE,MEANING FROM apps.mfg_lookups_v
WHERE lookup_type =  'BOM_AUTOCHARGE_TYPE') BACT
where mp.organization_id = bdept.organization_id
and mp.organization_code = '"&ORG&"'
and bdr.organization_id = bdept.organization_id
and bdr.department_id = bdept.department_id
and  bdr.resource_id = crc.resource_id (+)
and bdr.organization_id = crc.organization_id(+)
and 1 = crc.cost_type_id  (+)
AND BR.RESOURCE_ID = BDR.RESOURCE_ID
AND BRT.LOOKUP_CODE = BR.RESOURCE_TYPE
AND BACT.LOOKUP_CODE = br.autocharge_type"
, CommandTimeout=#duration(0, 0, 10, 0)]),
  #"Renamed columns" = Table.RenameColumns(Source, {{"EXTRACT_DATE", "Extract Date"}, {"DEPARTMENT_CODE", "Department Code"}, {"DEPARTMENT_DESCRIPTION", "Department Description"}, {"LOCATION_CODE", "Location Code"}, {"RESOURCE_CODE", "Resource Code"}, {"RESOURCE_DESCRIPTION", "Resource Description"}, {"UNIT_OF_MEASURE", "Unit of Measure"}, {"RESOURCE_RATE", "Resource Rate"}, {"RESOURCE_TYPE", "Resource Type"}, {"AUTOCHARGE_TYPE", "Autocharge Type"}, {"DEFAULT_BASIS_TYPE", "Default Basis"}, {"HOURS24_FLAG", "24 Hours Flag"}, {"LOCAL_EXTRACT_DATE", "Local Extract Date"}})
in
  #"Renamed columns";
shared Routing = let
  Source = Oracle.Database("COHREP", [HierarchicalNavigation=true, 
  Query="
  SELECT
    sysdate extract_date,
    from_tz(cast (sysdate as timestamp),'PST') at time zone '"&LocalTZ&"' local_extract_date,
    o.organization_code,
    msi.inventory_item_id,
    msi.segment1                                                                                                              item_number,
    cmsi.segment1                                                                                                             common_routing_item,
    decode(r.cfm_routing_flag, 1, 'Y', '')                                                                                    flow_routing,
    r.completion_subinventory                                                                                                 completion_subinventory,
    (
        SELECT
            l.concatenated_segments
        FROM
            apps.mtl_item_locations_kfv l
        WHERE
                l.subinventory_code = r.completion_subinventory
            AND l.organization_id = r.organization_id
            AND l.inventory_location_id = r.completion_locator_id
    ) completion_locator,
    ro.operation_seq_num                                                                                                      operation_seq_num,
    ro.standard_operation_code                                                                                                std_op_code,
    replace(replace(replace(ro.operation_description, CHR(124), ' '), CHR(13), ' '), CHR(10), ' ')                            operation_description,
    bd.department_class_code                                                                                                  dept_class_code,
    ro.department_code                                                                                                        dept_code,
    replace(replace(replace(bd.description, CHR(124), ' '), CHR(13), ' '), CHR(10), ' ')                                      dept_description,
    decode(ro.option_dependent_flag, 1, 'Y', 'N')                                                                             option_dependant,
    ro.operation_lead_time_percent/100                                                                                            operation_lead_time,
    ro.effectivity_date                                                                                                       effective_date,
    ro.disable_date                                                                                                           disable_date,
    decode(ro.count_point_flag, 1, 'Y', '')                                                                                   count_point,
    decode(ro.autocharge_flag, 1, 'Y', '')                                                                                    autocharge,
    decode(ro.backflush_flag, 1, 'Y', '')                                                                                     backflush,
    decode(ro.check_skill, 1, 'Y', '')                                                                                        check_skill,
    ro.minimum_transfer_quantity                                                                                              min_transfer_qty,
    rr.resource_seq_num                                                                                                       resource_seq_num,
    decode(res.resource_type, 1, 'Machine', 2, 'Person',
           4, 'Miscellaneous', 5, 'Amount', 6,
           'Currency') resource_type,
    decode(res.cost_code_type, 4, 'Y', 'N')                                                                                   osp_ressource,
    rr.resource_code                                                                                                          resource_code,
    replace(replace(replace(res.description, CHR(124), ' '), CHR(13), ' '), CHR(10), ' ')                                     resource_description,
    decode(rr.basis_type, 1, 'Item', 2, 'Lot')                                                                                basis,
    rr.uom                                                                                                                    unit_of_measure,
    rr.usage_rate_or_amount                                                                                                   usage_rate_or_amount,
    (
        SELECT
            resource_rate
        FROM
            apps.cst_resource_costs
        WHERE
                resource_id = rr.resource_id
            AND cost_type_id = 1
    ) resource_cost,
    decode(rr.available_24_hours_flag, 1, 'Y', 2, 'N')                                                                        dept_resource_available_24_hrs,
    rr.schedule_seq_num                                                                                                       schedule_seq,
    rr.substitute_group_num                                                                                                   substitute_group_number,
    rr.assigned_units                                                                                                         assigned_units,
    decode(rr.schedule_flag, 1, 'Yes', 2, 'No',
           3, 'Prior', 4, 'Next') schedule_flag,
    rr.resource_offset_percent/100                                                                                                resource_offset,
    decode(rr.autocharge_type, 1, 'WIP move', 2, 'Manual',
           3, 'PO receipt', 4, 'PO move') charge_type
FROM
    apps.bom_operational_routings     r,
    apps.bom_operation_sequences_v    ro,
    apps.bom_operation_resources_v    rr,
    apps.mtl_system_items_b           msi,
    apps.mtl_parameters               o,
    apps.bom_resources                res,
    apps.bom_departments              bd,
    apps.mtl_system_items             cmsi
WHERE 1 = 1
    AND ( r.routing_sequence_id = ro.routing_sequence_id
          OR r.common_routing_sequence_id = ro.routing_sequence_id )
    AND ro.operation_sequence_id = rr.operation_sequence_id (+)
    AND msi.inventory_item_id = r.assembly_item_id
    AND msi.organization_id = r.organization_id
    AND o.organization_id = r.organization_id
    AND res.resource_id (+) = rr.resource_id
    AND bd.department_id (+) = ro.department_id
    AND cmsi.inventory_item_id (+) = r.common_assembly_item_id
    AND cmsi.organization_id (+) = r.organization_id
and o.organization_code = '"&ORG&"'
"
, CommandTimeout=#duration(0, 0, 10, 0)]),
  #"Renamed columns" = Table.RenameColumns(Source, {{"EXTRACT_DATE", "Extract Date"}, {"ORGANIZATION_CODE", "Organization Code"}, {"ITEM_NUMBER", "Item Number"}, {"COMMON_ROUTING_ITEM", "Common Routing Item"}, {"FLOW_ROUTING", "Flow Routing Flag"}, {"COMPLETION_SUBINVENTORY", "Completion Subinventory"}, {"COMPLETION_LOCATOR", "Completion Locator"}, {"OPERATION_SEQ_NUM", "Operation Squence"}, {"STD_OP_CODE", "Standard Operation Code"}, {"OPERATION_DESCRIPTION", "Operation Description"}, {"DEPT_CLASS_CODE", "Department Class Code"}, {"DEPT_CODE", "Department Code"}, {"DEPT_DESCRIPTION", "Department Description"}, {"OPTION_DEPENDANT", "Option Dependant Flag"}, {"OPERATION_LEAD_TIME", "Operation Lead Time"}, {"EFFECTIVE_DATE", "Effective Date"}, {"DISABLE_DATE", "Disable Date"}, {"COUNT_POINT", "Count Point Flag"}, {"AUTOCHARGE", "Autocharge Flag"}, {"BACKFLUSH", "Backflush Flag"}, {"CHECK_SKILL", "Check Skill Flag"}, {"MIN_TRANSFER_QTY", "Minimum Transfer Quantity"}, {"RESOURCE_SEQ_NUM", "Resource Sequence"}, {"RESOURCE_TYPE", "Resource Type"}, {"OSP_RESSOURCE", "OSP Resource Flag"}, {"RESOURCE_CODE", "Resource Code"}, {"RESOURCE_DESCRIPTION", "Resource Description"}, {"BASIS", "Resource Basis"}, {"UNIT_OF_MEASURE", "Resource UOM Code"}, {"USAGE_RATE_OR_AMOUNT", "Resource Usage Rate"}, {"RESOURCE_COST", "Resource Cost"}, {"DEPT_RESOURCE_AVAILABLE_24_HRS", "24 Hours Resource Flag"}, {"SCHEDULE_SEQ", "Schedule Sequence"}, {"SUBSTITUTE_GROUP_NUMBER", "Substitute Group Number"}, {"ASSIGNED_UNITS", "Resource Assigned Units"}, {"SCHEDULE_FLAG", "Resource Schedule Flag"}, {"RESOURCE_OFFSET", "Resource offset"}, {"CHARGE_TYPE", "Resource Charge Type"}, {"LOCAL_EXTRACT_DATE", "Local Extract Date"}}),
  #"Changed column type" = Table.TransformColumnTypes(#"Renamed columns", {{"Resource offset", Percentage.Type}, {"Operation Lead Time", Percentage.Type}})
in
  #"Changed column type";
shared ORG = let
  ORG = "SPG" meta [IsParameterQuery = true, IsParameterQueryRequired = true, Type = type text]
in
  ORG;
shared LocalTZ = let
  LocalTZ = "Asia/Singapore" meta [IsParameterQuery = true, IsParameterQueryRequired = true, Type = type text]
in
  LocalTZ;
